---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service | Joner Football" description="Joner Football terms of service. Terms and conditions for using jonerfootball.com and the Joner Football App.">
  <section class="min-h-screen bg-joner-black py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-500 font-body text-sm mb-12">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-10">

        <!-- 1. Acceptance -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed">
            By accessing or using jonerfootball.com, the Joner Football App (app.jonerfootball.com), or any services provided by Joner Football, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with these terms, do not use our services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 2. Services -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">2. Services</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed">
            Joner Football provides football training content via a subscription-based app, in-person training programs in Sydney, global training camps, coaching workshops, and related digital and physical products. Our services are designed for players, coaches, and parents who want to improve their football through structured, technique-focused training.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 3. Subscriptions and Billing -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">3. Subscriptions and Billing</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed mb-4">
            App subscriptions are billed on a monthly or annual basis depending on the plan you choose. Key terms:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 font-body">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Free trials last 7 days. Cancel before the trial ends to avoid being charged.</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Subscriptions automatically renew at the end of each billing period.</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> You can cancel your subscription at any time through your Uscreen account.</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Payments are processed securely by Stripe via the Uscreen platform.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- 4. Refund Policy -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">4. Refund Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed">
            We do not offer refunds on subscription payments once they have been processed. If you experience technical issues that prevent you from accessing your subscription content, contact us at <a href="mailto:leejones@jonerfootball.com" class="text-joner-red hover:underline">leejones@jonerfootball.com</a> and we will work to resolve the issue. Camp bookings and event registrations have their own refund terms which are communicated at the time of booking.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 5. Intellectual Property -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed">
            All content on the Joner Football App and website, including but not limited to videos, training programs, drills, session plans, images, graphics, and text, is owned by Joner Football and protected by copyright. You may not share, reproduce, distribute, sell, or create derivative works from our content without prior written permission. Your subscription grants you a personal, non-transferable licence to access and view the content for your own training purposes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 6. User Conduct -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">6. User Conduct</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed mb-4">When using our services, you agree to:</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-300 font-body">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Not share your account credentials with others</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Not record, download, or redistribute app content</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Behave respectfully in any community features or live sessions</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-joner-red font-bold flex-shrink-0">&#8226;</span> Provide accurate information when creating your account</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed mt-4">
            We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 7. Limitation of Liability -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed">
            Joner Football is not liable for any injury sustained while following training programs, drills, or exercises provided through our app, website, camps, or in-person sessions. All physical training carries inherent risk. Always train within your physical limits and consult a medical professional before beginning any new exercise program. Parents and guardians are responsible for supervising minors during training.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 8. Governing Law -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">8. Governing Law</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed">
            These Terms of Service are governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of New South Wales, Australia. Any disputes arising from these terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of New South Wales.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 9. Contact -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white uppercase mb-4">9. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed mb-2">
            If you have any questions about these terms, contact us:
          </p>
          <div class="text-gray-300 font-body leading-relaxed">
            <p>Joner Football</p>
            <p>20 Narabang Way, Belrose NSW 2085, Australia</p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:leejones@jonerfootball.com" class="text-joner-red hover:underline">leejones@jonerfootball.com</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
